decks.notes: This deck focuses on utilizing graveyard synergy to quickly generate a large board presence and overwhelm the opponent with powerful creatures like Stinkweed Imp, Ichorid, and Hollow One. By utilizing cards like Bazaar of Baghdad and Golgari Thug to fill the graveyard, along with spells like Creeping Chill and Noxious Revival to trigger powerful effects, this deck aims to quickly set up a winning board state. Additionally, the deck includes disruption in the form of Force of Will and Force of Negation to protect its combo pieces and ensure its game plan goes off smoothly.

This deck focuses on generating a large amount of mana quickly using cards like Mishra's Workshop, Moxen, and Mana Crypt, and utilizing cards like Paradoxical Outcome and Mystic Forge to draw through the deck and set up a powerful combo. The goal is to assemble the Time Vault and Voltaic Key combo, or use Tinker to search for key artifacts like The One Ring or Coveted Jewel to create an overwhelming advantage and win the game in a single turn. The artifacts enable powerful synergies and provide immense value, ultimately leading to a swift victory.
